Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:12.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:21.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Chocolate Planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Chocolate {\i1}Planets{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:25.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed, we are Chocolate {\i1}Planets{\i0}, thank you for having us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, although it may be asking too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone please look here \N-What what what
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:37.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does everyone know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a deep-sea monkfish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:41.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right, a deep-sea monkfish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:43.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know the characteristics of this fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has a glowing light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:47.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know why it glows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:49.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because they want to attract other small fish to them \N -That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:54.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Deep-sea monkfish glow from the top of their heads to feed on the small fish that are attracted to it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:58.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time we bring you a theory about deep-sea monkfish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:00:59.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:04.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Deep-sea monkfish traps also work for humans
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, I'm a little confused about what you mean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:11.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it? Give me an example
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:15.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, it glows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:17.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And fish are attracted to it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the deep-sea monkfish eats them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:21.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Does this apply to humans as well?" That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this apply to humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-In humans, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:25.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does this apply to humans?  \N-In humans, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The kid on that side, you speak first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:28.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That means I'm not very credible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:30.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let the {\i1}planets{\i0} speak
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:32.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am the planet \N -That is, the monkfish will glow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:33.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a light, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:35.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then humans come along
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then they are preyed upon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:39.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Preyed upon...? \N-Can it eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is the trap for humans also light?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's light, it's light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:50.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That is, whether deep-sea monkfish can prey on humans \NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:53.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was just asking what everyone thinks, so I raised this question
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Were you uncomfortable just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:58.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No discomfort, no discomfort- \N-Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:00.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are just wondering why they can't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:02.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:04.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to watch the VTR at home, is that OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be like {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:11.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Coming up, the horror of the deep-sea monkfish prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:14.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also, we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:19.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No-one can tell who you are if you're wrapped in 10 rubber bands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:20.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,WHO THE HELL ARE YOU!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:25.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And, "If the person who is pranked pisses themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:28.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The instigator's face will instantly turn serious"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And, the "No couples sleep in bunk beds" verification!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:56.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Verify that the deep-sea monkfish's trap also works for humans
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:03:00.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time the stage is this warehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:07.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First, we contacted the targets under the guise of a fake program
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then suddenly let the venue expereince a blackout
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:15.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this time, the deep-sea monkfish machine hidden behind the wall of boxes appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:21.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Illuminated only by the tip of its tentacle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:25.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the target is attracted, it will be preyed upon instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah I see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, the first target
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishimura \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:37.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Viking's Nishimura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:46.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's completely unaware that on the other side of the wall, there is a giant deep-sea fish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:55.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishimura is confirming the playing cards that will supposedly be used in the next challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just when he is, for some reason, checking the smell of the cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoa scary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:13.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pretty scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't see anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A power outage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why just {\i1}this{\i0} reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not even a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not making a single sound is pretty impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it was me I'd probably be more afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Deep Sea State \N-Deep Sea State, absolutely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:31.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the staff wearing night vision goggles quietly remove the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:38.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the darkness, within the deep sea setting, a deep-sea monkfish appears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's pitch black
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really dark, can't even see the monkfish itself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:46.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishimura can't see anything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The camera is really powerful isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's finally speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The reaction to the power outage was rather uneventful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we go  \N-It's bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:06.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A single light in a sea darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:11.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, the view that Nishimura saw was this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:13.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd go closer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's leaning over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:28.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishimura is slowly drawn to the light
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're really good at leaning over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:32.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Once you get close...\N-That's all it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's ready to eat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Feeding begins immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How does it hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:44.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, what, what, ah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is how it happens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's how it happens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:58.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah~ so cold
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah~ slippery and slimy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The digestive juices enter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah~ so slimy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this, feels smelly and sticky and smelly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Back into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a turd \N-Yeah, a turd
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excreted through the anus
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:20.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been excreted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:24.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think just happened?  \N-Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:28.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think is going on here?  \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Firstly, you are on Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What...what is this? What theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What theory? It's a theory right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What...what? What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:45.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"The deep-sea monkfish trap also applies to humans"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A deep sea monkfish is that monkfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The one at the bottom of the sea? \N-Yes, the slimy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah this ah ah um
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The glowing one? \N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The one with the thing is the deep-sea monkfish?  \N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's the deep-sea monkfish ? \N-Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The light? \N-Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It leads things toward it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:08.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After I got close, my feet got stuck and it moved
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was it eating \N-So I was eaten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:13.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I was in it's stomach. This is gastric juice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You understand so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:21.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then I've been digested \N-Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:26.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the darkness, if light appears then you feel safer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's no one that wouldn't take the bait
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:32.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, isn't this the deep-sea monkfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't see it before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wa--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This, this, this, this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is how I was staring at it just now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:42.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one can escape from this, can they
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impossible to escape from
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is an awesome theory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:47.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The deep-sea monkfish is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to go home straight away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And look up "deep-sea monkfish" in the encyclopedia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Regardless of whether it works for humans
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:59.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or whether it is even possible to avoid it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The deep-sea monkfish device is chilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:05.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really interesting when leaning over
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The second target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please sit here for a moment, I'll call the director
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah~ Shiraki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Ah~ Shiraki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The candle's flame
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:27.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She practices the scenes of a fake script with great care despite the messy outfit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:32.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And despite the messy outfit, she is very careful regarding hygiene
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah~ Shiraki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She may be more wary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.86,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The scallops are about to be preyed upon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then...
