Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary, scary, scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something seems to be coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:10.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Different to Nishimura, the sensitive to sounds and movement man and woman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:14.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
