Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The light is on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You would lean toward it \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,While treading carefully, she walks ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really impossible to see anything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't see anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't see what's in front of her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Slowly moving towards the light
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:39.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Leaning over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:42.61,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's still relying on that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:47.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one also, unsurprisingly, went onto the tongue of the monkfish
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still a bit further, still a bit further
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The feeding begins
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it time to begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary... scary ah ah ah ah what is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eaten
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:22.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:22.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a prank, right? A prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:29.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, we divulge the theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:31.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know the deep-sea monkfish?  \N-I've heard of it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uses this to lure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah this is a universal object is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:43.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Went in the direction of the light
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, how do you feel about this lubricant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've used it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's good stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,First use
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:56.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think I understand the type of people who like this...
