Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The rest of what I want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:06.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will appear after the commercial break
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\alpha40}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Start with "Sorry"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't end with "Sorry"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target of the deep-sea monkfish prank is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mou Chugakusei (Already a high school student)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:44.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After darkness descends
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The wall is moved as before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the deep-sea monkfish debuts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then, this time too
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Getting closer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely closer than before
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:05.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:08.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, as he is already in range...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because the light is on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:15.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It hurts, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:25.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,More digestive juices were put in this time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No! What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:38.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because of the darkness, I've been feeling nothing but fear
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are from Wednesday Downtown \N-EH?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wednessy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wednessy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:46.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is Wednessy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Deep-sea monkfish prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, really, it's a deep-sea monkfish lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:59.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The design is so good its a pity you can't see it in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:02.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was really attracted to this orange light
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only this orange light could be relied upon to move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:07.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you would like to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:11.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah~ actually, I was really looking forward to doing the show I thought I was here for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"The support group is here today, too"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's self-made
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"For the sake of everyone, let's go..." or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:16.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah it's self-made
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:24.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hasegawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:27.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're not doing anything weird, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone says "Excuse me!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The power is out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As always, this time too
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks like a different person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His expression is so stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does look stupid \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:53.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Drawn by the only bright light in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You see, looks so stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bad, bad, bad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's pouring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The quantity is very good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:26.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's what happened, I was eaten  \N-That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:27.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next time I'll eat instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,M-1 Champion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the final individual is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This guy is pretty weird
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His use of words might be pretty bad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, he must be eaten
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:54.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Excuse me--!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is really what a bad guy looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The power is out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This guy doesn't even look frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems to have tripped
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd usually scream a little, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:06.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Failing to spot the light, he wanders around for 3 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why can't he find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand either
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's so dark maybe he can't see it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happened all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The panic is starting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Restlessness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:29.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What what what what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:39.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh, ahhhh, snake, snake, snake, snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still hasn't figured it out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:41.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, there are snakes ah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Snakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:41.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not snakes but digestive juices
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What, what, what, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:58.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time is based on the concept that the gastric juices will digest the clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Additional elements on top of the original
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:17.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is "the trap of the deep-sea monkfish applies to humans as well"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:20.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The one just now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like an orange ball \N-Light
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:30.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was very restless and moved closer to the light
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And I was eaten
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it was the only one that lit up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:39.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then, because I was eaten, I was digested in the stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:42.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's why it's so sticky
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:49.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H3732FF&}To sum up\N{\r}The trap of deep-sea monkfish is inescapable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome \N-So {\i1}that's{\i0} what it was all about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does everyone think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In short, 100% of the people were lured
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Monkfish are doing some amazing things at the bottom of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:05.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So this is probably how it happens to all the fish that are preyed upon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No idea what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That works for fish
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it won't work for comedians again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:13.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After this broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After watching it, even if...
