Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The light part?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:24.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Replace it with something like putting a colored thing in a place where there's nothing else
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a deep-sea monkfish
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So strict!
