Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:42.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Tamura Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:45.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time i've brought
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A theory about rubber bands
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:58.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A person with 10 rubber bands stretched over their face cannot be recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Frequently featured in shows
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is seeing many rubber bands can be stretched onto the face in 1 minute
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stuff like a Guinness World Record challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pretty common, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has anyone here done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've done it \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The face is deformed after putting it on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:19.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's super deformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:25.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With about 10 rubber bands, no one will be able to recognize the person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can 10 be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:30.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, let's verify it now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Right now? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The set has already been prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please move over there for the on-site verification
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:39.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Team Quiz - Who is the Person Disguised by Rubber Bands?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, the teams are divided into Matsumoto and Hamada teams
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory will be tested in the form of a quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also on this side is the comedian that will never turn down any work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Flirty comedian Fujimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:55.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Be careful of your choice of words
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by flirty comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:02.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One team will be presented with other team's rubber band-tied face
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And will be able to confer with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:04.49,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1066,157)}Matsumoto team's rubber bands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Up to 20 rubber bands can be used
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you succeed in making your opponent guess incorrectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:16.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The number of rubber bands used subtracted from 20 is the score
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:23.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, if the other team gets it right, they get zero points
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:27.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So if you can't guess with 5 bands, you get 15 points
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah it's this type of rule
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't understand at all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You 'aint your standard idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't help it, too old
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's already the age where his driver's license will be cancelled
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about, idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's still too early for that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna confuse the acceleration for brake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, for the first round of rubber bands tied to the guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:46.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Both of the participants are male
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We have A or B
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:52.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'll ask Matsumoto and Hamada to choose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Either is fine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:55.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let the other side choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:57.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're choosing B?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't let each other see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So each has decided their respective guests
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:07.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Got a good one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:09.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We don't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:13.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next two teams move quickly backstage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And are given rubber bands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where are the features of the face...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:19.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's the nose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The eyes have to be strained and deformed \N-The eyes are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:25.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lift the nose up or pull it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's better to put it up \N-Put it up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:34.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first to attack is Hamada's team
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Matsumoto's team guesses
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, ready to go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:41.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada's team used how many rubber bands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:42.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So few
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A very light touch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada's team... OPEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So hard \N-Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:56.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is just 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:57.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The amount is low
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's tough \N-Let's discuss it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:02.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this really just with 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble \N-This person's original foundation is too tough
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We did it in such a short time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I know the answer and still can't even see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fujimon you know loads of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No idea at all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no such person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:21.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very good
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:23.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well  \N-That's a win
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No clue at all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,May I speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:28.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not a formal answer \N-Not a formal answer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,FUNKY's Kato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's not right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:33.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would he come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:34.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can he do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's not lacking work, right? \N-I couldn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:38.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,COWCOW's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:44.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With the rubber bands it does look similar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:49.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have to rewind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:50.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have to imagine what it was like before the rubber bands were put on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's almost time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:52.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:53.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's kind of close
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:54.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:56.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, that's him. That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:00.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:01.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suddenly it came to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:04.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you ready? Team Matsumoto, please give your answer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:08.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miyashita Kusanagi's Miyashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:09.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miyashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:13.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miyashita Kusanagi's Miyashita, did you guess correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.82,0:22:18.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now let's have the guest remove the rubber bands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:20.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:21.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A face like this with just 8
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:26.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This this this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:28.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't see it now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:30.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then please take off the rubber bands  \N-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:31.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:36.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a big change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did we get it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:43.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still don't know yet, ah don't know yet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:44.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:47.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The correct answer is Miyashita Kusanagi's Miyashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:48.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:49.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto's team answered correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Barely got it right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:52.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:55.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:57.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Guessed correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:22:59.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:00.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Guessed it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:00.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:03.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I first saw it, I really couldn't tell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:04.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miyashita, how did the rubber bands feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:07.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being constricted by the rubber bands is surprisingly painful
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:08.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But in comparison to the rubber band,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Backstage, Hamada said "Don't move"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:13.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And at the same time hit me here, which was much more painful
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:14.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My apologies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.74,0:23:22.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So Hamada, who started the game, did not receive any points
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:23.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Matsumoto's team
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:24.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many rubber bands did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:26.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:28.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An aggressive approach
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:28.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course we're going to attack
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:29.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:31.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Matsumoto's team... OPEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:34.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:36.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very good
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:37.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:39.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're a little too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:42.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:43.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not good. This is not good
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:45.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who {\i1}is{\i0} this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:48.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please keep your face close
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is he a grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:52.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no sense of freshness  \N-No sense of fresh meat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.91,0:23:55.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This... this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:56.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,WHO THE HELL ARE YOU!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:58.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes!  \N-Don't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:00.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't describe people like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:01.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:02.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems to be completely unclear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:03.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a grandpa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:05.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, I think he may not be {\i1}that{\i0} old
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:06.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not that old?  \N-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:07.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's what i'm thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:09.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Guess someone at least
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:10.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:11.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just now she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:15.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I guess it's pretty similar
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:16.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Quite similar
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:17.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Go for it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:19.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is nothing else \N-Nothing else
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:20.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:21.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really can't tell
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:22.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't recognize them!
