Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.62,0:41:25.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three-tier bed!? \N-I've never heard of one!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.70,0:41:26.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three-tier bed? \N-That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.53,0:41:29.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My two sons and I sleep in this three-tier bed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.47,0:41:34.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The top is the second eldest, the middle is me, and the bottom is the third eldest
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.94,0:41:39.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The bottom pulls out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.38,0:41:42.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you pull it out when it's time to sleep?  \N-Yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.52,0:41:44.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At first, my three sons slept here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.42,0:41:48.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But since my oldest son is no longer at home, I sleep in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.09,0:41:54.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The second eldest is 26, I'm 49, and the third eldest is 24
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.76,0:41:57.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are all adults now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.45,0:41:57.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone is an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.84,0:42:01.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Total age: 197 years
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.02,0:42:04.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Spread across a total of five beds
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.47,0:42:06.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why add the years together
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.71,0:42:12.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although several groups of adults sleeping in bunk beds were found
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.44,0:42:15.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are there really no couples?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.04,0:42:17.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah... \N-The main topic
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.22,0:42:18.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.88,0:42:22.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next group of adults that sleep in bunk beds are...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.64,0:42:23.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this image!?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.80,0:42:27.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This 36-year-old woman who lives in Akita Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.36,0:42:31.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How do you use this bunk bed when you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.33,0:42:34.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I sleep on the bottom and my husband sleeps on the top
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.50,0:42:37.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To sum up, finally
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.63,0:42:41.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We found a bunk bed couple
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.74,0:42:45.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, the way they fall asleep is a bit strange
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.33,0:42:49.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The orientation of their heads is not the same
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.99,0:42:56.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the man is very happy with the current bunk bed state
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.63,0:43:00.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He peeks from above to see if I'm awake
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.90,0:43:03.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And seems very happy when he does it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.07,0:43:07.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think the person who invented the bunk bed is really too awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.97,0:43:11.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But, why did you decide to use this bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.37,0:43:15.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We took it over because originally it was for our children
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.58,0:43:19.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every day they fought about who would sleep on the top bunk
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.11,0:43:24.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep on top! \N-Today is my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.49,0:43:25.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this footage necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.68,0:43:28.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not needed, not needed, we all understand
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.49,0:43:29.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Concerning who sleeps on the top bunk, they often pulled and shoved each other next to the ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.57,0:43:29.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This makes it very easy to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.36,0:43:31.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And also the one in the lower bunk kicks the one above from below
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.81,0:43:33.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,To make it more visually appealing, the VTR was prepared for the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.21,0:43:35.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's good to have such things to be able to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.91,0:43:38.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.59,0:43:39.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.88,0:43:43.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Day and night the siblings argued endlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.04,0:43:42.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So there was an upward kick
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.78,0:43:45.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, much easier to understand with the VTR
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.17,0:43:52.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's enough you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.95,0:43:58.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If this continues, then father and I will sleep on the bunk bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.40,0:44:00.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right, didn't she just say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.35,0:44:03.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.88,0:44:07.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.80,0:44:16.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the two adults slept on the bunk bed while the children slept on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.90,0:44:18.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In all of the current findings
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.47,0:44:24.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every family originally bought the bunk beds for their children
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.92,0:44:30.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Apart from this couple, who now live in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.25,0:44:33.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Soon after the wedding I asked for a bunk bed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.46,0:44:38.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it's reasonable for us not to interfere with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.26,0:44:43.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since my wife requested it, I had to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.16,0:44:48.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In summary, there are two types of couples
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.64,0:44:53.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.40,0:44:55.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Couples sleeping in bunk beds
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.88,0:44:57.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.53,0:45:00.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the VTR recreation...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.50,0:45:03.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It didn't have much content
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.25,0:45:05.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not so much a matter of it not having much content, more that it wasn't necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.11,0:45:06.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not needed, not needed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.89,0:45:10.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously what the hell, that VTR was so annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.48,0:45:12.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, what was so annoying about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.32,0:45:16.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We shot the VTR in order to make the audience understand the situation more clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.43,0:45:19.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think the audience for this show is expecting that kind of VTR
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.66,0:45:23.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Explanations for layman aren't clear though
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.04,0:45:24.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, they said it quite clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.15,0:45:26.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was exactly the same as the picture I had in my head
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.75,0:45:29.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedians have more imagination though \N-Yes that's true
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.94,0:45:32.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The average person has nothing in their head \N-Yes, better brains
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.94,0:45:37.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a waste!  \N-The picture doesn't immediately come to mind
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.23,0:45:38.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not everyone can do it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.02,0:45:41.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has our program's staff been replaced?
